大局观 https://ritholtz.com资本市场、经济、地缘政治、科技、数字媒体的宏观视角2023 年 7 月 2 日星期日 11:48:44 +0000 en-US每小时1 https://wordpress.org/?v=6.2.2
 1971 德托马索·曼古斯塔https://ritholtz.com/2023/07/1971-de-tomaso-mangusta/Barry Ritholtz Sun, 02 Jul 2023 15:00:30 +0000 CarsWeekend https://ritholtz.com/?p=315587 <p>如果您了解 De Tomaso，可能是因为 Pantera。这款中置发动机、后轮驱动的跑车是意大利设计与底特律肌肉的完美结合。车身由 Carrozzeria Ghia 制造，动力装置为福特 V8。这是 De Tomaso 最受欢迎的汽车，从 1971 年到 1992 年生产了 7,000 多辆。直到……</p><p><a class="button" href="https://ritholtz.com/2023/07/1971-de-tomaso-mangusta/">阅读更多<i class="icon ion-arrow-right-c"></i></a></p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://ritholtz.com/2023/07/1971-de-tomaso-mangusta/">1971 年后的德托马索·曼古斯塔 (De Tomaso Mangusta)</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://ritholtz.com">《大图片》(The Big Picture)</a>上。</p> ; <p>如果您知道<a href="https://www.detomaso-automobili.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">De Tomaso</a> ，那可能是因为<a href="https://www.hotcars.com/de-tomaso-pantera-details/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Pantera</a> 。这款中置发动机、后轮驱动的跑车是意大利设计与底特律肌肉的完美结合。车身由 Carrozzeria Ghia 制造，动力装置为福特 V8。这是德托马索最受欢迎的汽车，1971 年至 1992 年间生产了 7,000 多辆。</p><p>直到最近，我对 De Tomaso Mangusta 还不熟悉。这是一种耻辱，因为这是一辆漂亮的汽车（正如其他人所说），它证明了汽车设计在 20 世纪 60 年代末和 1970 年代初达到了顶峰。</p><p>它由 296 bhp 的福特 V8 发动机提供动力，车身由 Giorgetto Giugiaro 设计，看起来像一辆真正的超级跑车，配有不寻常的鸥翼发动机盖。 “Mangusta”在意大利语中是猫鼬的意思，这种动物以杀死眼镜蛇而闻名。与卡罗尔·谢尔比（Carroll Shelby）的交易失败是这个名字的假定原因。</p><p>以下是<a href="https://petrolicious.com/articles/de-tomaso-mangusta" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Petrolicious</a>提供的 De Tomaso Mangusta 详细信息：</p><blockquote><p><strong>建成年份：</strong> 1967-1971<br /><strong>总产量：</strong> 401<br /><strong>发动机：</strong> 4.7L-5.0L 福特 V8<br /><strong>产生的功率：</strong> 221hp-306hp<br /><strong>产生的扭矩：</strong> 300lb-ft<br /><strong>车身设计：</strong> Giorgetto Giugiaro<br /><strong>整备质量：</strong> 2,612磅<br /><strong>新品价格：</strong> 11,500 美元</p></blockquote><p>下面看到的版本正在出售<a href="https://www.classicdriver.com/en/car/de-tomaso/mangusta/1971/971987" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Classic Driver</a> ，售价为 298,500 欧元（ <span class="price-amount-currency-value">324,350 美元）。</span></p><p>现在您所需要的只是一位了解 De TOmaso 的机械师以及您车库中的一些房间......</p><p></p><p></p><p> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-1.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-315613" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-1.webp" alt="" width="720" height="386" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-1.webp 1920w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-1-300x161.webp 300w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-1-1024x549.webp 1024w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-1-768x412.webp 768w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-1-250x134.webp 250w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/1-1-1536x823.webp 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2-4.jpeg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-315614" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2-4.jpeg" alt="" width="720" height="480" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2-4.jpeg 1800w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2-4-300x200.jpeg 300w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2-4-1024x683.jpeg 1024w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2-4-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2-4-250x167.jpeg 250w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/2-4-1536x1024.jpeg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3-3.jpeg" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-315615" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3-3.jpeg" alt="" width="720" height="480" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3-3.jpeg 1800w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3-3-300x200.jpeg 300w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/3-3-1024x683.